1. *Neverovatna* je tačnost ovog sata. (This watch's accuracy is *incredible*.)
2. Imala je *neverovatnu* ideju za novi projekat. (She had an *amazing* idea for a new project.)
3. Film je bio *neverovatan*! (The movie was *unbelievable*!)
4. *Neverovatnom* brzinom je pobegao od policije. (He escaped from the police with *astonishing* speed.)
5. Pogledaj ovaj zalazak sunca, boje su *neverovatne*. (Look at this sunset, the colors are *unbelievable*.)
6. *Neverovatno* je koliko brzo vreme prolazi. (It's *amazing* how time flies.)
7. Ona je *neverovatno* talentovana za ples. (She is *incredibly* talented at dancing.)
8. *Neverovatne* su mogućnosti koje nam pruža tehnologija. (The *amazing* possibilities that technology offers us are incredible.)
9. *Neverovatno* je koliko ljudi veruje u teoriju zavere. (It's *unbelievable* how many people believe in conspiracy theories.)
10. Prešao je *neverovatnih* 100 kilometara peške. (He walked *an incredible* 100 kilometers on foot.)